{"tid":1072421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"騎術學校「走馬」 棕馬屯門奔馳途人稱奇","createTime":"2019-03-22T04:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T12:48:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2db65309065905ee73fc20ff5f68acf4df5f575a","tid":1072421,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190322/large/1553223974_ffbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190322%2Flarge%2F1553223974_ffbb.jpg&h=20fd3984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190322/large/1553222752_2cbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190322%2Flarge%2F1553222752_2cbf.jpg&h=8869c008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190322/large/1553222754_e64c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190322%2Flarge%2F1553222754_e64c.jpg&h=6f9cace6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190322/large/1553222754_4a04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190322%2Flarge%2F1553222754_4a04.jpg&h=8f6b98e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於屯門龍門路的屯門公眾騎術學校，懷疑發生「走馬」事件，早上9時05分，有市民驚見一隻約1米長、頭頂及尾部有白毛的棕色馬，在湖翠路自由奔放地「慢跑」，只見牠跑得輕輕鬆鬆，姿態優美，即使在路上與的士擦身而過，亦完全無懼人與車，在湖翠路逕自跑了約300米兜圈轉入蝴蝶邨一所學校對開，最後由趕至的騎術學校職員將牠帶返行人路上，經安撫後再帶牠返回騎術學校，「走馬」過程約10至15分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n讀者吳先生當時正乘的士在湖翠路經過，在車廂赫見有馬在路上「跑馬」，「我離遠已經望到，睇真啲，真係有馬喺馬路上行，以前冇見過有馬走出嚟，所以都好震驚！佢自由奔放，冇馬繩，冇馬韁，冇人跟住，應該係附近騎術學校走出嚟，自己走甩咗，覺徥佢幾得意，但驚佢俾車撞，危險嘅，如果喺鬧市就唔得掂，又驚佢撞倒人，蝴蝶邨都好多老人家，萬一佢獸性大發，亂衝亂撞就唔好，如果有人俾佢撞倒一定瞓低！」<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n另一名讀者陳先生當時在美樂花園巴士站等車，突見到有隻馬在湖翠路兜圈去到蝴蝶邨，最後被職員趕至安撫及帶走。「佢跑嘅速度都快，咁啱冇咁多車，但對面有車就停低，之前冇見過有馬走出嚟，好多人見到都拍片影相，隻馬冇驚，好乖自己跑，街坊都話屯門最多都係見到牛，點知竟然有馬喺馬路！」<br />\n<br />\n由香港賽馬會管理的屯門公眾騎術學校於1994年1月4日落成啟用，佔地34800平方米，是全港規模最大的公眾騎術設施。學校設施包括辦公室、課室、一個大馬練習場及兩個小馬練習場、可容納78頭大小馬匹的馬房、更衣室、洗手間及停車場，另設有一條繞山而建，全長約950米的馬徑，讓學員得享野外策騎的樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190322/large/1553224606_036c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190322%2Flarge%2F1553224606_036c.jpg&h=a03f5768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門公眾騎術學校，懷疑發生「走馬」事件。張家豪攝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190322/59397181?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=url_copy&amp;utm_source=url_copy&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190322%2F59397181%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Durl_copy%26utm_source%3Durl_copy%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=819455d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190322%2F59397181%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Durl_copy%26utm_source%3Durl_copy%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=0c2508a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190322/59397181?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=url_copy&amp;utm_source=url_copy&amp;utm_content=share_link</a>"},{"pid":"903d7543b032c14319e68748ce227af26d1ded2b","tid":1072421,"uid":64601,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"真馬路"},{"pid":"f8623ffc1b359904fec68ed129dde4dbc77d40c1","tid":1072421,"uid":17008,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"903d7543b032c14319e68748ce227af26d1ded2b","tid":1072421,"uid":64601,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"真馬路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"馬諗：條馬路咁多車既"},{"