0322%2Flarge%2F1553222754_e64c.jpg&h=67738164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDC9:無野可以超越我前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dced46884f64ce263da698d3325dd5a734e37003","tid":1072421,"uid":237303,"like":1,"dislike":88,"score":-87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3394c399909549349896ad678ab929fefb026ab4","tid":1072421,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:57:33.000Z","msg":"最後由趕至的騎術學校職員將牠帶返行人路上，經安撫後再帶牠返回騎術學校.<br />\n<br />\n都唔知是職員安撫隻馬<br />\n定隻馬安撫職員<br />\n<br />\n如果隻馬是有錢佬的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbea9993994b27a41ac4f8fb9fa07250337a010","tid":1072421,"uid":133,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:00:32.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 千門八將(正將)"},{"pid":"2d67590208bf72a21946bd81a57ca5137d478507","tid":1072421,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:03:39.000Z","msg":"隻馬個樣好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b61c94bc577d7d83fb2e2002ea58d8e1e005925","tid":1072421,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53ac43d1eed29ee291df624d08f96d5d82f0a12f","tid":1072421,"uid":50124,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"隻馬幾靚仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfacUX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfacUX4.jpg&h=9c7b3091&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"要點度先度到隻馬得1米長"},{"pid":"0235a4627dbd8be435b492d2aa825734114298e7","tid":1072421,"uid":4780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"53ac43d1eed29ee291df624d08f96d5d82f0a12f","tid":1072421,"uid":50124,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"隻馬幾靚仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfacUX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfacUX4.jpg&h=9c7b3091&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"Yuuuuuu~~~~ good girl ~~~~~~ 🚬"},{"pid":"e5cc2f37e9f67c37aa711600fc45131fd19e8338","tid":1072421,"uid":65887,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"【上海賽馬集體出逃 公路慢跑】<br />\n<br />\n上海金山區星期一凌晨，有九匹馬走上漕廊公路慢跑。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查後發現，馬匹是區內一個馬場所有。馬場負責人陸先生隨後趕到，將馬匹帶走。陸先生指這幾匹馬都是比賽用的馬，價格非常昂貴。<br />\n因馬棚門沒關好，馬匹遂乘機出逃。<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2054849464632989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2054849464632989&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=b332cb6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2054849464632989</a>"},{"pid":"d06eab16929626f129c67f8e3da37d30f1e0899e","tid":1072421,"uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.portal-pokemon.com/play/resources/pokedex/img/pm/cb874883fcffc227e8d065e275221e1e05ece46c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.portal-pokemon.com%2Fplay%2Fresources%2Fpokedex%2Fimg%2Fpm%2Fcb874883fcffc227e8d065e275221e1e05ece46c.png&h=1c658ee9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7c8ff166c2e84d9456dab95e3331c1ca27ad188","tid":1072421,"uid":169992,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"有無「看花」"},{"pid":"16c1d4dddff3be03b54be93d3f8ccc9853349e85","tid":1072421,"uid":83992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"咁鬼馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4724c1d1a5362d2ee8df12b04d51fc999c2b19f8","tid":1072421,"uid":59328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cde83668c13c4484dbeb3f45ab59fa5abed3fd29","tid":1072421,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:47:06.000Z","msg":"隻馬好似熱鬥小馬"},"cite